---
const CTA_URL = "https://helpmaton.com";
---

<div
  class="mt-14 pt-10 border-t border-green-500/20 not-prose"
  aria-label="Sponsored: Helpmaton"
>
  <p class="text-green-300/90 text-base leading-relaxed mb-3">
    <strong class="text-green-400 font-['Orbitron'] tracking-wide"
      >Building with AI agents?</strong
    >
    Helpmaton gives you workspaces, agent memory, budget controls, and
    webhooks—without the lock-in. It’s source-available so you can self-host when
    you need to. Quick integrations for Gmail, Notion, Slack, Discord, and others.
  </p>
  <a
    href={CTA_URL}
    target="_blank"
    rel="noopener noreferrer"
    class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-green-500/15 text-green-400 font-['Orbitron'] text-sm tracking-wide px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg border border-green-400/40 hover:bg-green-500/25 hover:border-green-400/60 transition-colors"
  >
    Try Helpmaton
    <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
  </a>
</div>
